xxl.comparators
Class FeatureComparator

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--xxl.comparators.FeatureComparator
public class FeatureComparator
extends Object
implements Comparator

The FeatureComparator compares the 'feature's of two given Objects. The feature of each Object is extracted with a mapping-Function, i.e. this classs implements the compare-method as follows: 

	public int compare (Object o1, Object o2) {
		return comparator.compare(function.invoke(o1), function.invoke(o2));
	}
